SOVEREIGN AGENTIC GATEWAY (SAG) CONFIGURATION
Algorand Node Connection (Testnet)
We recommend using AlgoNode or a local sandbox
ALGOD_SERVER=https://testnet-api.algonode.cloud
ALGOD_TOKEN=aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
ALGOD_PORT=443

Agentic Trust Anchor (Wallet)
This account must be funded with Testnet ALGOs to sign transactions
AGENT_MNEMONIC="your secret twenty four word mnemonic phrase goes here"

Hardened Environment Settings
Port for the Rust-based gateway API
GATEWAY_PORT=8080

Minimal Alpine Linux log levels (error, warn, info, debug, trace)
LOG_LEVEL=info

DPDP Compliance Settings
Set to 'true' to enable strict PII data scrubbing in memory buffers
ENFORCE_DPDP_PRIVACY=true
